				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$10\,\mathrm {W/m}^2$$\end{document} and used typical meteorological year (TMY) data averaged from 2005 to 2020 from the PVGIS-ERA5 dataset [20].

